    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are committed to complete transparency with every potential buyer. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint finish is flawless, with a deep, rich luster that shows no scratches, chips, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces are perfectly intact. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows zero wear, all surfaces are pristine, and every button, knob, and screen functions exactly as it did from the factory. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and full service history available. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and drivetrain \u2014 are in perfect working order. The tires retain excellent tread depth and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for and truly earns the 'mint' designation. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed.",
